          "thinking": "Now I have the policy. The key clauses for duplicate reimbursement are:\n1. Clause 第十条: 同一发票最多报销1次。发现同一发票在不同报销单中重复出现的,应认定为重复报销风险。\n2. Clause 第十一条: 不得将同一事项或同类事项拆分为多笔报销以规避审批权限。\n\nNow I need to check the expense records for the 财务管理部 (D009) to see if there are any duplicate reimbursements.Let me look at the expense records for the 财务管理部 (D009).",
